vuls.name: CVE-2021-25329
vuls.desc: The fix for CVE-2020-9484 was incomplete. When using Tomcat with a configuration edge case that was highly unlikely to be used, the Tomcat instance was still vulnerable to CVE-2020-9494.

vuls.name: CVE-2022-33043
vuls.desc: A cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability in the batch add function of Urtracker Premium v4.0.1.1477 allows attackers to execute arbitrary web scripts or HTML via a crafted excel file.

vuls.name: CVE-2022-32119
vuls.desc: Arox School ERP Pro v1.0 was discovered to contain multiple arbitrary file upload vulnerabilities via the Add Photo function at photogalleries.inc.php and the import staff excel function at 1finance_master.inc.php.

vuls.name: CVE-2022-34244
vuls.desc: Adobe Photoshop versions 22.5.7  and 23.3.2 are affected by an Access of Uninitialized Pointer vulnerability that could lead to disclosure of sensitive memory.

vuls.name: CVE-2022-34243
vuls.desc: Adobe Photoshop versions 22.5.7  and 23.3.2 are affected by a Use After Free vulnerability that could result in arbitrary code execution in the context of the current user.

vuls.name: CVE-2021-34203
vuls.desc: D-Link DIR-2640-US 1.01B04 is vulnerable to Incorrect Access Control. An attacker can easily use telnet to log in, modify routing information.

vuls.name: CVE-2018-5380
vuls.desc: The Quagga BGP daemon (bgpd) prior to version 1.2.3 can overrun internal BGP code-to-string conversion tables used for debug by 1 pointer value, based on input.

vuls.name: CVE-2022-30929
vuls.desc: Mini-Tmall v1.0 is vulnerable to Insecure Permissions via tomcat-embed-jasper.

vuls.name: CVE-2022-22965
vuls.desc: Spring MVC or Spring WebFlux application running on JDK 9+ may be vulnerable to remote code execution (RCE) via data binding.

vuls.name: CVE-2021-44079
vuls.desc: In the wazuh-slack active response script in Wazuh 4.2.x before 4.2.5, untrusted user agents are passed to a curl command line, potentially resulting in remote code execution.

vuls.name: CVE-2021-26068
vuls.desc: An endpoint in Atlassian Jira Server for Slack plugin from version 0.0.3 before version 2.0.15 allows remote attackers to execute arbitrary code via a template injection vulnerability.

vuls.name: CVE-2021-20845
vuls.desc: An issue was discovered in Mattermost Server before 5.18.0. It allows attackers to cause a denial of service (memory consumption) via a large Slack import.
